{"tid":1322431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戒嚴下香港可隨時被封網","createTime":"2019-07-16T02:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T02:57:09.000Z","uid":125349,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"240bca4b2ac9fb118df3b43e8e2bab29a47cb0c2","tid":1322431,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"在法律的層面，有兩條條例限制切斷網絡的情況出現，包括《電訊條例》106章13條指，若行政長官認為已發生緊急情況，可簽署手令接管或使用電訊電台，或對其加以控制，手令有效期不多於一週，但可以連續每週發出。條例沒有列明何謂「緊急情況」。另一條《緊急情況規例條例》241章2條指，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬緊急情況或危害公安的情況時，行政長官會同行政會議可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例」。</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">換言之，不管是全港性的封網，或者是局部地區封網，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港都需要進入「緊急狀態」才能要求互聯網服務提供者斷網。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/20141002a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F20141002a&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a18e57a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F20141002a&h=7ff85e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/20141002a</a>"},{"pid":"79f315a5649137a6a373805e908eef24295eacf7","tid":1322431,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"Come on baby<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3fcd99b75a005b6bcc52903d9d3986a985f7ea","tid":1322431,"uid":144883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇得上網會有咩後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b04901b695b06b514a3adcc3d065f983c53d509","tid":1322431,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"冇網上會唔會700萬人上街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a727d769dfd8ee8f3a90eb5908c08732fc600037","tid":1322431,"uid":18691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"Home office 係咪仆街？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1198603dbb2c7a939044a8f7132a53ce7c5e2b19","tid":1322431,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"要準備三樣嘢 利申: 科技嘅嘢我識條鐵咩<br />\n1) 官方出海外文宣得返記者 要記者有網路向海外發訊 例如要準備衛星電話<br />\n<br />\n2) 疑有戒嚴要向領事館埋手 因為到時可能得返領事館有對外通訊<br />\n睇下可唔可以俾記者或授權入內通訊<br />\n<br />\n另外亦要領事準備於戒嚴狀態解放陣會入城 希望各國考慮牽制方案<br />\n<br />\n3) 建立現場指揮系統同行動順序<br />\n<br />\n當區指揮:<br />\nA) 大量WALKIE 要連接到各大(1)及(2)區同伴<br />\nB) 旗幟名令<br />\nC) 戒嚴下已經不能再和理非!! 但亦切記唔可能有兵力增緩 陸路交通必然受阻 以無退路<br />\n<br />\n誇區行動:<br />\nA) 如接獲當區戒嚴 就要鄰區就要立即出發<br />\n- 鎖金鐘 旺角出動<br />\n- 鎖旺角 銅鑼灣出動<br />\n- 鎖銅鑼灣 沙田上水大圍出發<br />\nB) 請勿落單並制定集結點 同區分A/B位 按當區巴絲自發制定平常容易集結嘅點<br />\nC) 陸路交通必然受阻 遍遠區域如需增緩可能要事前部署 可能需要制定另一套行進方式 應考慮如單車等助步工具"},{"pid":"2313341e946fef52ce887eae2477748d0dda75bb","tid":1322431,"uid":245064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"係就快唔好等下個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n我一個國際金融大城市戒嚴喎,你係就快,我睇你班大媽沙輸幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f60e2331c4b7a2fe81bedd682b0e27f67c8465d","tid":1322431,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a727d769dfd8ee8f3a90eb5908c08732fc600037","tid":1322431,"uid":18691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"Home office 係咪仆街？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"連remote都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}